{"tid":1968372,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"武漢肺炎》台灣醫療援助已抵達 帛琉大使再發文感謝台灣","createTime":"2020-04-11T15:27:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T16:00:41.000Z","uid":227801,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"990cab41cfd2fa4375a7045ed1c48649e3934e9c","tid":1968372,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T15:27:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3130282\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3130282&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1WxVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=3a6ae7d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3130282&h=a71a6f53\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3130282</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/04/11/php3SeoPc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F04%2F11%2Fphp3SeoPc.jpg&h=7532d4ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2020-04-11 12:05:12<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕武漢肺炎疫情全球爆發，我國協助太平洋友邦帛琉，載運呼吸器和生物安全櫃等醫療物資的漁船已在凌晨運抵當地。對此，帛琉駐聯合國常任大使鄔露彤（Ngedikes Olai Uludong）在推特上發文再次感謝台灣，表示這批物資將完善帛琉的檢測設施，並註記「#TaiwanCanHelp」，肯定「台灣能幫忙」的精神。<br />\n<br />\n帛琉駐聯合國常任大使鄔露彤今日凌晨在推特上表示，載有呼吸器和生物安全櫃等醫療物品的台灣援助漁船已抵達帛琉，這批物資可幫助完善當地的檢測設施，她表示「這是一個好消息！」也再次感謝台灣的幫助。<br />\n<br />\n帛琉駐聯合國常任大使鄔露彤曾多次透過推特感謝台灣的醫療援助，1日台灣派出的醫療物資包機隨2位醫護專家抵達帛琉時，她感性寫道，「在帛琉不斷向國際求援時，只有台灣伸出援手」，稱讚是「患難時的真朋友」。幾日後也再次感謝台灣醫療專業人才的幫助，並在推文中註記「#TaiwanCanHelp」。此次援助漁船再展現台帛「兄弟之邦」在醫療防疫上的友好合作，以及「台灣能幫忙」的精神。"},{"pid":"53d5879ae92928d8529168e60ad00983621bf489","tid":1968372,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T15:28:12.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"31e0f538cbd78422c1c909a91def1b51a9538d46","tid":1968372,"uid":126283,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T15:28:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FtOmtLL.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFtOmtLL.gif&h=9fdb6e28&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9473fab7d3efe85dd39d76e3e325cfcc82f2772","tid":1968372,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T15:33:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6023b0831516cc0910b115285e936cb089b76ceb","tid":1968372,"uid":105924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T15:34:59.000Z","msg":"我係臺灣人呀屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1aee7f50a0f49e5708f6449b00513748b53b73b","tid":1968372,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T15:39:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd29995d470420814a6fe74ba3b51fe5fa1deba5","tid":1968372,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T15:51:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4af86f3d4a2cb2fd4a1c9f6b8b454426a20e48f","tid":1968372,"uid":279463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T16:00:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}